race.comment: ASTON TERESA (6) recorded back to back wins before finishing sixth last time after copping a check in the run, finishing a 5 length sixth (19.85) in a Grade 5 at Hobart. Key player on best form. KIWI MAKAVELI (1) was in the money again last start when second at this track (29.97). Can feature with the right run. LAST SPLASH (5) hit the frame last time at this track but the start prior rocketed around 600m at this track in 34.86. Rates a leading chance if runs up to recent winning time. SPLENDID HERA (3) collected a minor prize last start over this track and distance - must be considered.
